{
  "stem": "3666.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I think that the Jews were also not allowed to shop in certain shops, and not getting the right kind of food anymore.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You had like cards and rations and--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] It went--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- they came in, in June.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1941.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in September, the ghetto was already created.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So within these three months, a lot of people didn't even enter the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Vilna had about close to 80,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And each Jew, or family rather, got a special certificate, like [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And those people who lived in the poorer sections didn't even enter the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The ghetto could-- could not accommodate 80,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what they did, and a lot of my family disappeared right away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We later on, we knew that they were slaughtered at Ponary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ponary, what was Ponary?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ponary was a forest, outside of Vilna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they just picked a spot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they used to shoot them down like dogs in mass-- in mass graves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- almost my entire-- my father's entire family lies buried in Ponary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not part the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What they did was part of the ghetto, which they picked the poorest part in Vilna, like [NON-ENGLISH], I think it was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had some names of streets there, very narrow little streets, and really a poor section.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Jews who lived and had businesses in those sections were actually removed overnight, all the families.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took them, I think to Ponary, and created space for the people who came in, like ourselves, who lived in the better and little more moderate section, not rich-rich.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, we were not rich.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We lived very nice, you know, in a nicer area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they made room for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
